03:22.242 --> 03:24.244
Come see what I got for ya!

03:24.744 --> 03:26.246
Come on, Deke, come on!

03:27.747 --> 03:28.748
Aah!

03:57.277 --> 03:59.279
I thought we told you

03:59.314 --> 04:01.281
to stop working our
precinct, Early Riser.

04:01.316 --> 04:03.283
We got bigger fish to fry.

04:03.318 --> 04:05.785
You do your trickin'
somewhere else.

04:12.792 --> 04:14.294
Is that my-

04:17.332 --> 04:20.300
Deke!
Deke!

04:38.818 --> 04:40.820
Is everybody here
having a good time?

04:43.323 --> 04:44.603
How about that weather up there?

04:44.824 --> 04:45.864
Is it fine enough for you?

04:47.827 --> 04:49.829
How about me?
How about Deke, your man?

04:51.831 --> 04:52.832
How about me?

04:53.333 --> 04:55.335
How about me?

04:55.835 --> 04:56.836
How about me?

04:56.871 --> 04:58.838
Yeah!
Yeah!

04:58.873 --> 05:00.840
Am I big enough for you?

05:15.855 --> 05:18.358
18 months ago...

05:18.393 --> 05:20.433
I was down on my knees in
the white man's jailhouse.

05:20.860 --> 05:21.861
Mmm!
Yes!

05:21.896 --> 05:25.365
I wasn't down on my knees
in the jailhouse to pray.

05:25.400 --> 05:26.400
No!
No!

05:26.866 --> 05:29.369
I wasn't even down on
my knees to shoot craps.

05:29.404 --> 05:30.870
Ha ha!
Ha ha!

05:30.905 --> 05:32.872
Deke O'Malley
was down on his knees

05:33.373 --> 05:34.874
in the white man's jail

05:35.375 --> 05:36.376
cleaning out the
white man's toilet bowl!

05:36.411 --> 05:37.411
No!
No!

05:37.877 --> 05:39.379
All right!

05:39.414 --> 05:42.882
So l-i asked the Lord
to help me!

05:42.917 --> 05:44.884
To show me the way!

05:44.919 --> 05:46.886
And bless my soul, he did!

05:46.921 --> 05:47.921
Yeah!
He did!

05:47.922 --> 05:50.390
The Lord come to me in a dream!

05:50.425 --> 05:53.893
He said,
"Deke, I want to use you

05:53.928 --> 05:56.396
like I used Noah of old!"

05:56.896 --> 06:01.401
He said, "Deke, I want you
to build an ark

06:01.436 --> 06:02.902
and sail my people home!"

06:03.403 --> 06:04.404
Yeah!
Yeah!

06:04.439 --> 06:06.906
And there she is, Black Beauty!

06:08.408 --> 06:09.909
Are you black enough to hear me?

06:12.412 --> 06:13.913
Amen! Amen!

06:13.948 --> 06:15.915
For 3 months now,

06:15.950 --> 06:18.918
in Detroit, Chicago,
Los Angeles,

06:18.953 --> 06:20.420
Baltimore, Washington,

06:20.455 --> 06:22.422
people have been
standing in line,

06:22.457 --> 06:23.923
waitin' and waitin'

06:23.958 --> 06:27.427
for a chance to get
on board black beauty.

06:27.462 --> 06:30.430
'Cause, Brothers,
we are going home.

06:31.931 --> 06:34.434
Good-bye, rats and roaches!

06:34.934 --> 06:37.937
Good-bye being
kicked and low-rated!

06:37.972 --> 06:40.940
Good-bye getting
robbed and cheated!

06:40.975 --> 06:44.444
Good-bye having to live
on the white man's welfare!

06:44.479 --> 06:45.479
Right on, Brother!

06:45.945 --> 06:47.947
We are going home.

07:01.961 --> 07:04.964
Come on! Next!
What's your name, Miss?

07:04.999 --> 07:06.966
You'll find salvation.

07:07.001 --> 07:09.969
How the hell did he
get a permit for this?

07:10.004 --> 07:11.971
Lieutenant says
it's a race leap.

07:12.472 --> 07:14.474
It's doing good for his people.

07:14.509 --> 07:16.476
Thank you, Reverend O'Malley,
thank you.

07:16.511 --> 07:18.478
We're going home

07:18.513 --> 07:21.981
all going home

07:22.016 --> 07:23.983
we're going home

07:29.489 --> 07:31.991
we're going home

07:32.026 --> 07:35.495
going home

07:35.530 --> 07:39.499
we're going home

07:39.534 --> 07:43.002
there you go.
Thank you.

07:43.037 --> 07:46.506
But, sir, the minimum
down payment is $100.

07:46.541 --> 07:48.508
Oh, please, ma'am.

07:49.008 --> 07:51.511
You don't want to break ol'
Uncle Budd's heart, do ya?

07:52.011 --> 07:56.516
$20. count it. It's all I
got in the world right now,

07:56.551 --> 07:59.018
but give me a chance.
Please, ma'am.

07:59.053 --> 08:01.020
Why not?

08:01.055 --> 08:03.022
Yeah, sure.

08:03.057 --> 08:04.057
Uncle Budd?

08:04.058 --> 08:07.527
Uncle Budd.
Yeah, Uncle Budd.

08:07.562 --> 08:08.562
There you go.

08:08.563 --> 08:10.029
Okay, step right up!

08:10.064 --> 08:12.532
God bless you, Brother.
God bless you, Brother.

08:21.541 --> 08:25.545
Well, if it ain't king
Kong and Frankenstein.

08:25.580 --> 08:28.548
Hey, ed, I didn't know these
cats was going back to Africa.

08:28.583 --> 08:31.583
They ain't. They're going right back
across the street where they come from.

08:31.586 --> 08:35.054
Only thing I hate worse
than a honky pig cop,

08:35.089 --> 08:37.056
and that's a nigger pig cop.

08:37.091 --> 08:39.558
What kind of talk
is that, soul Brother?

08:40.058 --> 08:43.062
Don't you know that
black is beautiful?

08:51.571 --> 08:53.072
Fly, baby.

08:53.107 --> 08:55.074
Just cool it.

09:02.582 --> 09:04.083
O'Malley?
Yes.

09:04.118 --> 09:06.586
We're from the D.A.'s
office. He wants to see you.

09:06.621 --> 09:08.588
D.A.'s office?
Well, I'm busy.

09:10.089 --> 09:11.089
Now! Let's go!

09:11.090 --> 09:12.091
Wait a minute, buddy!

09:12.126 --> 09:13.092
Let's see your credentials.

09:13.127 --> 09:15.094
Quit stalling, O'Malley.

09:15.129 --> 09:16.129
Black Judas!

09:16.130 --> 09:18.598
That's what you are!

09:19.098 --> 09:20.099
Honky!

09:20.134 --> 09:25.104
Now, now. I'm going
downtown right now

09:25.139 --> 09:27.607
and tell that white man's
district attorney

09:27.642 --> 09:30.610
that Deke O'Malley's gettin' sick
and tired of being pushed around.

09:32.146 --> 09:34.614
Keep it black till I get back.

09:34.649 --> 09:36.115
Ok, let's go.

09:50.129 --> 09:52.131
John! John!

09:52.166 --> 09:54.133
John!

10:15.154 --> 10:16.155
Get in!

10:33.673 --> 10:35.675
Don't you step on my ribs!

13:54.373 --> 13:56.876
Whoo! Hey, Sister,
come here!

14:58.472 --> 15:00.439
No, no, no, no!

15:59.498 --> 16:01.500
Ok, what do you want?

16:01.535 --> 16:03.502
Deke O'Malley.

16:03.537 --> 16:05.504
Yeah? And what's that
got to do with me?

16:05.539 --> 16:08.507
We ain't got O'Malley.
We sure as hell got you.

16:08.542 --> 16:12.011
Which means that sooner
or later, we got O'Malley.

16:12.046 --> 16:14.013
Is that black enough for ya?

16:14.048 --> 16:15.514
What do we got here?

16:18.552 --> 16:21.520
We know how finicky the good
Reverend is about his wardrobe,

16:21.555 --> 16:25.024
so he oughta be scootin' up
here any minute to change.

16:25.059 --> 16:28.527
Hey, ed, dig these fine vines.

16:28.562 --> 16:32.531
Mmm! And on your po' policeman's
salary, you can't afford it.

16:32.566 --> 16:33.566
Ain't that awful?

16:33.567 --> 16:35.534
What a shame. Not a single one your size.

16:35.569 --> 16:38.537
Now, wait a minute. I think this
Italian suit here'll work for me.

16:39.038 --> 16:40.039
Thing of beauty.

16:40.074 --> 16:41.540
What's this here?

16:43.042 --> 16:45.044
Bless Jesus.

16:45.079 --> 16:49.548
A silk hat for occasions.
My, my.

16:49.583 --> 16:52.551
What sacrifices he makes
for his po' starvin' people.

16:53.052 --> 16:55.054
He sure do.

16:58.057 --> 17:00.059
Now, somebody shot up
O'Malley's barbecue

17:00.559 --> 17:04.063
and made off with 87 grand
of poor people's money.

17:05.564 --> 17:08.067
Who?

17:08.102 --> 17:11.069
The question is... who?

17:11.105 --> 17:13.571
Whoever it was just Missed.

17:13.607 --> 17:17.076
Another couple of inches, and we would've
brought you his brains in a saucer.

17:17.111 --> 17:19.078
Oh, yeah? Who did it?

17:19.113 --> 17:20.579
I just asked you that.

17:20.614 --> 17:23.582
O'Malley ratted on the mafia.

17:24.083 --> 17:25.084
Remember?

17:25.118 --> 17:26.118
Could've been them.

17:26.119 --> 17:28.087
Them boys don't never forget.

17:28.587 --> 17:31.090
Could be his number's up,

17:31.125 --> 17:33.092
unless Digger and me
get to him first.

17:33.127 --> 17:34.127
Where is he?

17:38.597 --> 17:40.599
Well, how about it?

17:42.101 --> 17:45.604
Hidin' out,
he ain't got a chance, Iris.

17:45.639 --> 17:49.108
Deke O'Malley
always has a chance.

17:52.146 --> 17:54.113
Hello, betty?
Give me that!

17:54.148 --> 17:56.615
All right, O'Malley, do
yourself a favour and come in-

17:56.650 --> 17:58.617
you bitch!

18:02.121 --> 18:05.124
God damn it, ed, cool it!

18:05.159 --> 18:07.626
He's crazy.

18:07.661 --> 18:11.130
He's crazy. That son of a bitch
is crazy! I want him out!

18:11.165 --> 18:13.132
I got him, Iris.

18:13.167 --> 18:15.134
2 days, 2 weeks, 2 months.

18:15.634 --> 18:17.636
It's all the same.

18:17.671 --> 18:20.139
I'm nailing his ass to the wall.

18:21.140 --> 18:22.641
Be smart, Iris.

18:22.676 --> 18:26.145
Get off the boat
before we sink it.

18:36.155 --> 18:38.657
Ed. Digger.

18:40.659 --> 18:42.661
Something new on the O'Malley squeal. What?

18:42.696 --> 18:45.664
They found the meat truck and the
golden money wagon all smashed up.

18:46.165 --> 18:47.666
One got killed.
O'Malley?

18:47.701 --> 18:49.168
No.

18:49.203 --> 18:50.169
Lieutenant wants you two
guys up there right away.

18:50.204 --> 18:52.171
Where?
Harlem river yard.

18:52.206 --> 18:54.173
Oh, by the way, what's with her? She talk?

18:54.208 --> 18:57.676
No, but she's our main lead
to O'Malley, so watch her.

18:58.177 --> 18:59.678
Be cool, Brother.

18:59.713 --> 19:01.180
Jarema is hep.

19:01.215 --> 19:04.183
She's a stone fox.
Watch your ass.

19:04.218 --> 19:05.218
No sweat there.

19:21.700 --> 19:24.703
Found some confetti.

19:25.704 --> 19:27.206
Where's the loot?

19:27.706 --> 19:28.707
Ask O'Malley.

19:28.742 --> 19:31.710
I know how you feel about O'Malley. Do you?

19:35.714 --> 19:37.216
You make him?

19:37.251 --> 19:40.719
Yeah. He's a pickpocket
named Early Riser.

19:40.754 --> 19:42.221
He was at the rally.

19:42.256 --> 19:45.724
He works with a partner
named lo boy, a junkie.

19:46.725 --> 19:48.727
They worked the holy dream.

19:48.762 --> 19:51.230
Could be the militants, ed.
They hate O'Malley's guts.

19:51.265 --> 19:55.734
No. They wouldn't
pull a job like this.

19:55.769 --> 19:57.736
It ain't their style.

19:57.771 --> 19:58.771
Hey, ed!

19:58.772 --> 19:59.772
What is it?

19:59.773 --> 20:01.740
Look at this.

20:06.245 --> 20:09.748
Cotton from inside
the meat truck.

20:09.783 --> 20:12.751
It ain't drugstore cotton.

20:12.786 --> 20:14.253
What is it?

20:14.753 --> 20:17.256
It's raw, unprocessed cotton,

20:17.291 --> 20:19.758
like from a bale.

20:19.793 --> 20:25.764
Ah. It's a long time
since I seen cotton like that.

20:25.799 --> 20:28.267
Digger, you ain't never
seen no raw cotton before.

20:28.302 --> 20:31.770
You was born and raised right
here in New York, just like me.

20:31.805 --> 20:33.272
What the hell
are you two doing here?

20:34.773 --> 20:37.276
Digger found a hidden drop slot.

20:37.311 --> 20:40.279
This was in it.
It's full of trash.

20:40.779 --> 20:42.781
The syndicate.

20:42.816 --> 20:45.284
When O'Malley was with 'em, he
talked, and they threatened to get him.

20:45.319 --> 20:46.785
Why'd they wait?

20:47.286 --> 20:48.787
White guns comin' up here,

20:48.822 --> 20:50.789
trying to knock off
Reverend O'Malley, you think?

20:50.824 --> 20:52.291
Could be.

20:52.326 --> 20:56.295
Blacks find out about this,
there'll be hell to pay.

20:56.330 --> 20:59.298
I want round the clock police
protection for Reverend O'Malley.

20:59.798 --> 21:01.800
To hell with O'Malley!

21:01.835 --> 21:04.803
What about the $87,000
of poor black folks' money

21:04.838 --> 21:07.306
that he stole from all
over this country? Stole?

21:07.341 --> 21:08.807
That's right. Stole!

21:08.842 --> 21:10.809
We ran a check on
O'Malley's entire operation.

21:10.844 --> 21:12.811
It's clean.
Absolutely legitimate.

21:12.846 --> 21:15.314
Full clearance from
the state department,

21:15.349 --> 21:17.316
securities exchange comMission,

21:17.351 --> 21:18.817
the attorney general of the state
of New York. What else do you want?

21:18.852 --> 21:21.820
What the hell does the attorney
general, the state department,

21:21.855 --> 21:23.322
or even the president
of the united states know

21:23.357 --> 21:25.717
about one Goddamned thing that's
going on up here in Harlem?

21:25.824 --> 21:28.327
Ed O'Malley's respected by
responsible people. Respect, my ass!

21:28.362 --> 21:30.829
Pastors, race leaders,
politicians,

21:30.864 --> 21:33.332
not to mention the large following
he has among black folk everywhere.

21:33.367 --> 21:35.834
Black folk need hope
like everybody else.

21:35.869 --> 21:38.837
What is it with you people?

21:39.338 --> 21:42.341
One of you like Reverend
O'Malley tries to do something,

21:42.376 --> 21:44.343
does anybody try to help him? Hell no!

21:44.378 --> 21:46.345
You're after him
like crabs in a basket.

21:46.845 --> 21:53.352
Uh, how many shares of the back to
Africa, inc. Would you buy, captain?

21:53.387 --> 21:54.387
That's impertinent.

21:54.388 --> 21:56.355
The hell it is!

21:56.390 --> 21:58.357
One more word out of you, and
I'll run you right off the lot.

21:58.392 --> 22:00.859
We've been trying to teach
white folks all our lives.

22:01.360 --> 22:02.361
School's over.

22:02.396 --> 22:06.865
Let's go look for lo boy
at junkies' paradise.

22:11.370 --> 22:13.372
Damn it, Anderson. Who's in
charge of this investigation,

22:13.407 --> 22:14.407
you or them?

22:14.873 --> 22:15.874
You've gotta understand
ed and Digger, sir.

22:16.375 --> 22:18.377
I understand those two,
all right.

22:18.412 --> 22:21.380
Too quick with their fists,

22:21.415 --> 22:23.882
too flip with their talk,
too fast with their guns.

22:23.917 --> 22:26.885
They're two damn black maniacs
on a powder keg,

22:26.920 --> 22:28.887
and you're
letting them run wild.

22:28.922 --> 22:32.891
Ed and Digger, they have their own
special way of dealing with things up here.

22:32.926 --> 22:35.394
And if they find something
kinky on Reverend O'Malley,

22:35.429 --> 22:36.895
I've gotta respect it.

22:45.871 --> 22:47.873
Sister!
Yes?

22:48.373 --> 22:50.375
Good afternoon, Sister.

22:50.410 --> 22:53.879
And what kind of trick are you trying
to play on me, you Old Uncle tom?

22:53.914 --> 22:55.881
Ain't no trick, ma'am.

22:55.916 --> 22:58.884
I'm just trying to get this
bale of cotton onto my cart.

22:58.919 --> 23:00.385
Cotton?
Yes, ma'am.

23:00.420 --> 23:03.388
And I was just wonderin'
if some good, nice-lookin',

23:03.423 --> 23:07.392
strong Christian lady like
you wouldn't give me a hand.

23:07.427 --> 23:08.894
I am a Christian.

23:08.929 --> 23:11.897
That's why I don't take a
stick and knock your teeth out.

23:11.932 --> 23:13.899
All of you trying
to steal my money!

23:14.399 --> 23:15.901
Tryin' to steal your money?

23:15.936 --> 23:18.403
Yes! Trickers! That's what
you are. Every one of you!

23:18.438 --> 23:19.905
Why, you old fool!

23:19.940 --> 23:22.407
Don't you think
I got sense enough to know

23:22.442 --> 23:26.411
there ain't no such thing as
a bale of cotton in Harlem?

23:26.446 --> 23:28.413
Hmmph!

24:20.081 --> 24:23.084
That damn Bryce
chewin' my ass out.

24:23.119 --> 24:25.086
Dumb Anderson didn't say a word.

24:25.587 --> 24:28.089
Well, he's got his own
mortgage to worry about.

24:30.592 --> 24:33.094
I oughta quit this job.

24:33.129 --> 24:35.096
All right, now,
suppose you do quit.

24:35.131 --> 24:37.599
Suppose you tell 'em to
take the badge and shove it.

24:37.634 --> 24:38.600
Who's gonna pay your mortgage?

24:38.635 --> 24:40.101
You.
Mm-mm!

24:40.136 --> 24:43.104
Not me, baby.
You quit, I quit.

24:43.139 --> 24:45.607
Then who'll protect the black
folks from the white folks?

24:47.609 --> 24:51.112
Who's gonna protect the
black folks from themselves?

24:53.114 --> 24:59.120
I'm sick of this. Gotta be at
death's door. I'm tired of this jazz.

25:03.124 --> 25:04.125
God damn.

25:04.160 --> 25:05.627
Aah!

25:05.662 --> 25:07.128
When did you turn Japanese?

25:07.163 --> 25:09.631
Come on.
You know the position.

25:10.131 --> 25:11.371
Come on, spread your legs back.

25:11.633 --> 25:13.134
Finally got it together.

25:13.169 --> 25:14.636
We plan to keep it that way.

25:14.671 --> 25:17.639
This ain't no shooting gallery
no more. This is Swahili class.

25:17.674 --> 25:19.674
So why don't you guys
take your business and split?

25:19.676 --> 25:21.643
Io boy.

25:23.645 --> 25:27.148
Early Riser's partner.
We want him.

25:27.183 --> 25:30.652
Is he on Swahili, too?

25:30.687 --> 25:33.655
If that's who you want,
why don't you check Reba's?

25:43.199 --> 25:45.667
Where'd you learn them
dirty Swahili words?

25:46.167 --> 25:48.670
Ask your mama.

25:58.179 --> 26:00.682
How long you gonna
keep this up, Copper?

26:00.717 --> 26:02.684
Till it's over, Sister.

26:05.186 --> 26:08.690
It's been 4 hours now, and I'm
just sick of lookin' at you.

26:08.725 --> 26:11.693
You are really one ugly child.

26:11.728 --> 26:13.194
I mean, it's really too bad

